Key Match Events: Iraq's Muhammad Ali scored the winning goal in injury time to stun Vietnam 1-0
Pre-Game Insights: Vietnam and Iraq were expected to progress to the third qualifying round, and their clash would determine the group F winners
Post-Match Reflections: Coach Phillippe Troussier praised Vietnamese players for their courage but regretted the loss in injury time
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was part of the second qualification round of the 2026 FIFA World Cup at Hanoi's My Dinh National Stadium
